d\"\n|{{left}}August 10, 1977\n|{{left}}[[New York Cosmos (1970\u20131985)|Cosmos]]\n|A\n|3\u20130\n|57,828\n|\n|-\n|}\n\n== Statistics ==\n===Season scoring===\n''GP = Games Played, G = Goals (worth 2 points), A = [[Assist (soccer)|Assists]] (worth 1 point), Pts = Points''<ref name=\"Rowdies stats\" /> \n{| class=\"wikitable\"\n|-\n! style=\"width:35%;\"| Player\n! style=\"width:9%;\"| GP\n! style=\"width:9%;\"| G\n! style=\"width:9%;\"| A\n! style=\"width:9%;\"| Pts\n|- align=center \n| align=left |[[Derek Smethurst]]||21||19||4||42\n|- align=center \n| align=left |[[Rodney Marsh]]||24||8||11||27\n|- align=center\n| align=left |[[Steve Wegerle]]||25||5||11||25\n|- align=center \n| align=left |[[Davie Robb|David Robb]]||15||8||1||17\n|- align=center \n| align=left |[[Adrian Alston]]||17||7||3||17\n|- align=center \n| align=left |[[Wes McLeod]]||20||1||5||7\n|- align=center \n| align=left |[[Mark Lindsay (footballer)|Mark Lindsay]]||20||1||3||5\n|- align=center \n| align=left |[[Ars\u00e8ne Auguste]]||14||2||0||4\n|- align=center \n| align=left |[[Ian Anderson (Scottish footballer)|Ian Anderson]]||11||2||0||4\n|- align=center \n| align=left |[[Lenny Glover|Len Glover]]||19||0||3||3\n|- align=center \n| align=left |[[Mike Connell (soccer)|Mike Connell]]||26||0||1||1\n|- align=center \n| align=left |[[Dennis Wit]]||7||0||1||1\n|- align=center \n| align=left |[[Paul Hammond (footballer)|Paul Hammond]]||24||0||0||0\n|- align=center \n| align=left |[[Stewart Jump]]||22||0||0||0\n|- align=center \n| align=left |[[Kevin Eagan]]||21||0||0||0\n|- align=center \n| align=left |[[Farrukh Quraishi]]||14||0||0||0\n|- align=center \n| align=left |[[Joey Fink]]||13||0||0||0\n|- align=center \n| align=left |[[Boris Bandov]]||5||0||0||0\n|- align=center \n| align=left |[[Frantz St. Lot]]||5||0||0||0\n|- align=center \n| align=left |[[Winston DuBose]]||3||0||0||0\n|- align=center \n| align=left |[[Radomir Stefanovi\u0107]]||2||0||0||0\n|- align=center \n| align=left |[[Alex Pringle]]|